      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant even look at the news anymore. everything is just... breaking. fires, floods, the heat... it feels like we're just watching the clock tick down on the planet. what is even the point of trying to build a life or have a future when the world is literally dying? it feels so pointless to even exist right now.",
